for over two months. . .

00:29.640 --> 00:31.312
. . .and you've never spent the night.

00:31.480 --> 00:34.552
Well, go clean up the dead animals
and l'll come over tonight.

00:34.720 --> 00:36.551
Deal. l'll cook you dinner.

00:36.720 --> 00:38.312
Great.

00:41.840 --> 00:43.637
l think l love you, Charlie Harper.

00:47.280 --> 00:51.432
Thank you.
l'll see you later.

00:56.680 --> 00:58.477
Wait a minute.

00:59.200 --> 01:01.031
Did you just say ''thank you''?

01:01.600 --> 01:03.192
-Did l?
-Yes.

01:03.360 --> 01:07.399
