17:27.440 --> 17:29.795
Well, traditional therapy can help. . .

17:29.960 --> 17:33.555
. . .but you'll have to commit to a long,
arduous process of self-exploration. . .

17:33.720 --> 17:35.392
. . .over a period of years.

17:35.560 --> 17:40.839
Years?
l can't go years without Mr. Pee-pee.

17:41.000 --> 17:43.992
Charlie, isn't your long-term
mental and emotional health. . .

17:44.160 --> 17:46.879
. . .more important
than a few fleeting orgasms?

17:47.400 --> 17:50.437
lt's not even
more important than one.

17:51.920 --> 17:57.836
