could try a shortcut like hypnotherapy.

17:58.440 --> 18:00.556
-You know how to do that?
-l studied it.

18:00.720 --> 18:03.871
But for it to work,
you'd have to trust me completely.

18:04.720 --> 18:06.711
You know, Rose,
as strange as it may seem. . .

18:06.880 --> 18:10.634
. . .out of all the women l know,
you're the only one l trust at all.

18:11.440 --> 18:13.396
Personally, l find that very flattering. . .

18:13.560 --> 18:16.950
. . .while professionally,
it's deeply disturbing.

18:18.480 --> 18:19.993
Oh, well.

18:20.160 --> 18:25.996
So just relax, sit back,
close your eyes. . .

18:26.160 --> 18:29.232
. . .and listen only
to the sound of my voice.

18:29.640 --> 18:31.596
l wanna get my mother
out of my head, okay?

18:31.760 --> 18:34.354
l don't wanna quit drinking,
gambling or any good stuff.

18:34.960 --> 18:37.554
Got it. Okay.

18:37.720 --> 18:39.392
So just relax.

18:45.080 --> 18:48.470
Oh, my.
l see everything's back to normal.

18:48.640 --> 18:50.358
Better than normal.

18:50.520 --> 18:53.398
-Did you take one of those pills?
-l don't need any pills.

18:53.560 --> 18:55.391
lt's all me.

19:04.040 --> 19:05.678
And nobody else.

19:07.360 --> 19:10.955
Why don't you relax while l introduce
you to the new, improved Charlie?

19:23.920 --> 19:27.435
-Who were you calling?
-l was just ordering a little chicken.

19:37.040 --> 19:38.359
What smells so good?

19:38.920 --> 19:41.354
Your kid's in the kitchen baking.

19:41.520 --> 19:44.557
-You're kidding.
-Hey, Dad. Want a cupcake?

19:46.280 --> 19:48.077
Sure.

19:48.480 --> 19:50.038
Uncle Charlie?

19:50.200 --> 19:51.713
Thank you.

19:51.880 --> 19:55.077
Have as many as you want.
l've got another batch in the oven.

19:55.920 --> 19:58.593
That's very tasty.
What prompted this?

19:58.760 --> 20:03.197
l figured out l don't need a girlfriend.
lf l want a cupcake, l make it myself.

20:03.360 --> 20:06.397
Taking matters into his own hands.

